Our Clients
We work with a range of clients, from private investors to sovereign wealth funds. To meet our clients’ unique investing needs, we offer solutions that range from turnkey products to customized multi-asset portfolios.




 

ENDOWMENTS AND FOUNDATIONS
With roots in endowment investing, HighVista understands the needs and priorities of our endowment and foundation clients. Our globally diversified portfolios help protect and grow assets while carefully managing portfolio risk. We offer focused investment strategies or serve as the Outsourced Chief Investment Officer (OCIO), designing investment policy and managing all aspects of an institution’s investing and reporting needs.



 

Private Investors and Family Offices
Many of our most enduring relationships are with family offices and private investors. We understand the nuanced demands of inter-generational planning and are committed to helping our clients invest in a manner that protects and grows their assets. We understand that trusted advice is often the most valued asset, and we have earned an important role offering inputs well beyond the investment realm.



 

Sovereign Wealth Funds and Other Institutional investors
We have engaged with a range of institutions to help meet their long-term investment needs. For some, our mandate strives to provide an attractive return via our diversified risk-targeted funds, while for others we have developed a customized multi-asset solution. In each case, we also serve as an advisor to help senior management think about specific investments, asset allocation and portfolio management challenges across their organizations.










