HighVista Strategies LLC Key Developments

HighVista Strategies LLC Appoints Edmund A. Hajim as Chairman
Feb 21 17
HighVista Strategies LLC announced that Edmund A. Hajim has been appointed Chairman of the firm. Mr. Hajim has a distinguished career comprised of senior positions in investment banking, investment management and hedge fund management. Most recently, Mr. Hajim was the President of Diker Management, LLC, a New York City-based investment management firm. Mr. Hajim has served for the past six years on the Advisory Board of HighVista Strategies.


